# ─── Auto-generated / temporary markdown docs ────────────────────────────────
# These are AI-generated notes and should not be tracked in version control.
# Only README.md and docs/ folder markdown files are kept.
*.md
!README.md
!docs/**/*.md
!src/**/README.md

# ─── Design system internal docs (not user-facing) ───────────────────────────
src/shared/design-system/**/IMPLEMENTATION.md
src/shared/design-system/**/README.md
src/features/**/IMPLEMENTATION.md

# ─── Visual test / example files (dev-only) ──────────────────────────────────
src/**/*.visual-test.tsx
src/**/*.examples.tsx
